          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Custom Retail Bags Define your Brand</h3><p>Consumers can get a feel of your brand by a simple encounter with your custom retail gift bag. By seeing retail bags with your logo imprinted, your brand will be recognized as exclusive and unique.</p><p>Uploading your logo and adding custom imprinting hardly gets easier.  Select the wholesale gift bags of your choice, and click “add imprinting”.  With our streamlined process, your custom retail bags will soon be ready for carrying in style.</p><h3>Custom Bags for Small Businesses </h3><p>Premium branding that takes small businesses places shouldn't be hard to come by.  Through intentionally keeping printing minimums low, Allurepack provides access to small businesses to get custom gift bags with their brand prominently visible.</p><p></p><p></p>"
          }
        }
      },
