          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "The Fine Print of Custom Printed Bags",
            "text": "<p><strong>Plate Fee</strong> for imprinting on bags is  $89.</p><p><strong>Printing Fee </strong>for imprinting on bags is $60 for the first 200 prints.  Each additional print is $0.27.</p><p>The printing plate fee a is one time fee for the first time you print. Once we create a plate for you, you will only be charged for printing.</p>",
